  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      275.92,
      536.97,
      344.4
    ],
    "text": "On the morning of 19.04.2026, two individuals who sustained injuries in a sharp weapon assault near the Kataliyanpalla Bridge in the Ratnapura Police Division were admitted to the Ratnapura Hospital. Subsequently, the Ratnapura Police Station initiated investigations based on information received from the Hospital Police stating that one of the injured persons had succumbed to his injuries.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      358.84,
      439.66,
      372.12
    ],
    "text": "The deceased is a 38-year-old resident of Devalayagawa, Ratnapura.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      386.68,
      537.73,
      427.58
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary inquiries indicate that the deceased and the injured individual were returning home on 18.04.2026 after attending a musical show when they became involved in a dispute with another group.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      469.86,
      541.84,
      496.94
    ],
    "text": "The suspects connected to the incident have been identified, and further investigations are underway by the Ratnapura Police to apprehend them.",
